==Ugaritic==
===Noun===
'''ỉnr'''
# "[[Cur]]".  Exact meaning unclear, but used in parallel with ''[[klb]]'', dog.
#:''kklb bbtk n`tq, kỉnr ảp ḫštk''. Like a dog we enter your house, like a cur the entrance to your chamber.
====Related terms====
* ''[[klb]]'' (masc.)
* ''[[klbt]]'' (fem.)

